hw2: 3D Objects and 1st Person

Hours to complete: 15 hours

Evan Brookens
CSCI4229/5229 Summer 2016

Demonstrates how to draw objects in 3D.
Show a stary night with beds.

Key bindings
  m          Switch mode to model view to 1st person
  p          In model view switch from orthoganal and
  			 perspective modes
  arrows	 Change view anagle in model views
  			 Move camer in 1st person
  page up    Raise Dim
  page down  Lower Dim			 
  a          Toggle axes
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

 